cu.explanation_en: Setting ASN.1 verbosity to an invalid value will cause parsing errors during configuration loading and prevent proper initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting PDSCH antenna ports XP to zero will invalidate the antenna configuration and prevent proper downlink transmission setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PDSCH 天線端口 XP 設定為零會使天線配置無效，並阻止正確的下行鏈路傳輸設定。
